{"word":"H4054 - מִגְרָשׁ - migrâsh - mig-rawsh' - Cast out","slug":"H4054","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִגְרָשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>migrâsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mig-rawsh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cast out"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D4;</bdo>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - migra&#x0302;sh  migra&#x0302;sha&#x0302;h</b></b> - <i>mig-rawsh', mig-raw-shaw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1644\">H1644</a>; a <i>suburb</i> (that is, open country whither flocks are <i>driven</i> for pasture); hence the <i>area</i> around a building, or the <i>margin</i> of the sea: - cast out, suburb."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1644\">H1644</a>, <a href=\"#/H1645\">H1645</a>, <a href=\"#/H1646\">H1646</a>, <a href=\"#/H1647\">H1647</a>, <a href=\"#/H1648\">H1648</a>, <a href=\"#/H1649\">H1649</a>"}]}